
Common Issues and Solutions:

1. High Gas Costs
   路 Use batch operations (ERC-1155)
   路 Implement permit for gasless approvals
   路 Optimize storage patterns
   路 Use immutable variables where possible
2. Deployment Failures
   路 Check gas limits
   路 Verify constructor parameters
   路 Ensure deployer has sufficient funds
   路 Check network connectivity
3. Integration Issues
   路 Verify ABI matches contract
   路 Check network compatibility
   路 Test with different wallets
   路 Review error messages
4. Security Concerns
   路 Run security analysis tools
   路 Review access controls
   路 Check for reentrancy
   路 Validate all inputs

Maintenance Checklist

Weekly

路 Monitor gas usage trends
路 Check for security updates
路 Review error logs
路 Backup configuration

Monthly

路 Full security review
路 Gas optimization review
路 User feedback analysis
路 Documentation updates

Quarterly

路 Third-party security audit
路 Major version review
路 Compliance check
路 Performance benchmarking

Getting Help

Support Channels:

路  Documentation: Check /docs/ folder first
路  Community: GitHub Discussions
路  Bugs: GitHub Issues
路  Security: security@gitdigital.com

When Asking for Help:

1. Include contract address
2. Share error message
3. Specify network
4. Describe what you tried
5. Include relevant code snippets
